Package: logging
Title: A Logging Package
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: person("Mario", "Frasca", email = "mariotomo@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: logging is mostly based on Python logging, it offers
             hierarchic loggers, multiple handlers per logger,
             level based filtering, space for custom formatters.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
License: GPL 3+
